      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in reliable running order. The engine exhibits a heavy knock and significant oil leaks, while the transmission struggles to engage properly in higher gears. Externally, the body shows extensive rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and clear coat failure across the hood and roof. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and non-functional electronics including the radio and climate control. This car is best suited as a major project or a parts donor for a similar model.",
