      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly diamond in the rough? This vehicle is ready for some TLC and offers a great opportunity for anyone handy with tools! While it shows significant wear and needs some mechanical and cosmetic repairs, it\u2019s an affordable way to get started on your next automotive adventure!",
