      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. It\u2019s the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend adventures. I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
