    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 centers around the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. The power is managed by a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS system refresh and a reinforced rear subframe, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The chassis remains composed with upgraded Bilstein dampers and refreshed control arm bushings. While displaying honest patina, the mechanical synchronization and compression remain within factory tolerances, providing a visceral, analog performance profile.",
