    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a refined luxury SUV that has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive shape. The exterior paint retains a deep, brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper, typical of light, respectful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the genuine leather upholstery is supple and free of cracks or stains, and the genuine wood trim remains vibrant. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and power tailgate, operates exactly as it should. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust. It has a comprehensive service history, with recent oil changes and brake inspections completed. It drives smoothly with the quiet composure Lexus is known for. This is an excellent opportunity to own a high-tier vehicle that has been cared for with pride. Includes two keys and original owner manuals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
